NAME: Van Gogh Museum
TIPS: A museum dedicated to the works of Vincent van Gogh, with the largest collection of Van Gogh's paintings and drawings in the world.

NAME: AMAZE Amsterdam
TIPS: An interactive art exhibit that features illusions, games, and puzzles that challenge visitors to think outside the box.

NAME: Nxt Museum
TIPS: A contemporary art museum that focuses on the intersection of art, technology, and design.

NAME: Ripley's Believe It or Not!
TIPS: An interactive museum that features a collection of oddities, curiosities, and other unique items from around the world.

NAME: Anne Frank House Museum
TIPS: A museum dedicated to the Jewish girl Anne Frank, who hid from the Nazis during World War II in a secret annex of this building.

NAME: BODY WORLDS Amsterdam
TIPS: An exhibition that features real human bodies and body parts, preserved through a process called plastination, to educate visitors about anatomy, health, and disease.

NAME: Hemp Gallery
TIPS: A gallery that showcases the history and culture of hemp, with a collection of hemp-related artifacts, interactive exhibits, and educational programs.

NAME: Heineken Experience
TIPS: A brewery tour and interactive exhibition that explores the history and brewing process of the Heineken beer brand.

NAME: Stedelijk Museum
TIPS: A museum of modern and contemporary art that features works by artists like Vincent van Gogh, Jackson Pollock and Salvador Dalí

NAME: The Stopera
TIPS: The Municipal Theatre & City Hall, a cultural center that houses two of Amsterdam's main performance venues, the Stadsschouwburg and the Muziektheater.

NAME: NEMO Science Museum
TIPS: A hands-on science museum that aims to make science and technology accessible and fun for visitors of all ages.

NAME: The Dutch National Opera & Ballet
TIPS: A national theater and opera house that features performances of traditional and contemporary works, as well as ballet and other dance performances.

NAME: The Amsterdam Pipe Museum
TIPS: A museum that explores the history and culture of smoking pipes and pipe-making, with a collection of pipes from around the world.

NAME: The Foam Fotografiemuseum Amsterdam
TIPS: A photography museum that showcases contemporary and historical photography, as well as hosting temporary exhibitions.

NAME: The Pianola Museum
TIPS: A museum that explores the history and technology of the pianola, a type of player piano, with a collection of pianolas, rolls and other related items.

NAME: The Museum Het Schip
TIPS: A museum that explores the history and architecture of the Amsterdam School, a Dutch architectural style from the early 20th century.
